<p>The Bethel area's newer construction typically features more solar-ready roof designs and modern electrical systems that simplify installation. West Eugene neighborhoods often benefit from reduced tree shading and favorable south-facing roof orientations. The River Road corridor's mix of housing types creates opportunities for both traditional rooftop solar and ground-mount systems. Downtown Eugene's urban density may limit solar options for some properties, but the area's walkability can reduce overall energy consumption needs.</p>

